all tournament at the Pierre Mauroy stadium on Sunday, July 28.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_C\", \"score\": 0.7351763023297633, \"rank\": 0.34149233106936283, \"text\": \"Group C\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_C\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_C\"}, {\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Mauroy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre Mauroy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Mauroy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Mauroy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA fielded one of the strongest rosters in its history, featuring the likes of 39-year-old LeBron James, Steph Curry, Anthony Davis, and Kevin Durant, who's a three-time Olympic gold medalist.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999381544, \"rank\": 6.082649324368962e-11, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steph Curry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\"}, {\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.133083855025594e-39, \"text\": \"Anthony Davis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\"}, {\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.110064833297899e-24, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those big names delivered, with Durant leading the way with 23 points on 8-of-9 shooting.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"James collected 21 points, 7 rebounds, and 9 assists as Jrue Holiday added 15 points.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.117531300039908e-22, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jrue_Holiday\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jrue Holiday\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jrue_Holiday\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jrue_Holiday\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To have KD (Durant) on my side is a treat for sure,\\\" said James.\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dissociation_constant\", \"score\": 0.9969007162587071, \"rank\": 0.002911028138458181, \"text\": \"KD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dissociation_constant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dissociation_constant\"}, {\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.117531300039908e-22, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Devin Booker scored 12, Curry fired 9 of his 11 points from beyond the arc, as newcomer Anthony Edwards also shot 11.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1167, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.05865956800801e-38, \"text\": \"Devin Booker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\"}, {\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.8852849693611267, \"rank\": 0.1266663796691376, \"text\": \"Anthony Edwards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three-time NBA MVP Nikola Jokic powered Serbia with 20 points, 5 rebounds, and 8 assists.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1326, \"end\": 1332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999997919644773, \"rank\": 1.5183374633166656e-07, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Serbia started well and refused to buckle under the pressure of the Americans, with the NBA's Denver Nuggets and silver medalist Jokic leading the way.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999997919644773, \"rank\": 1.5183374633166656e-07, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.16488878736075e-24, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver_Nuggets\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.051050727047075e-44, \"text\": \"Denver Nuggets\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver_Nuggets\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver_Nuggets\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the fluidity of coach Steve Kerr's US team and their potent combination of old stalwarts James, Durant, and Curry proved too much for the Europeans.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1556, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Kerr\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\"}, {\"begin\": 1569, \"end\": 1571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4624933822385e-18, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.117531300039908e-22, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Durant and James shooting perfectly in the first half, the Americans held a 58-49\\u00a0advantage at the break before pulling away by the third quarter, 84-65.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.117531300039908e-22, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Durant dropped 21 points, firing 5-of-5 from three-point range and also a perfect 8-of-8 shooting clip in the first two quarters.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"James had 12 points on 5-of-5 field goal and 5 assists by halftime.\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.117531300039908e-22, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the best game we have played so far (including pre-Olympic exhibition games).\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought they tested us early,\\\" said James.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.117531300039908e-22, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[The atmosphere] was phenomenal.\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Listening to our national anthem, listening to the fans cheer, definitely got a little nervous, my stomach, the butterflies came out, it was different,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"James is at his fourth\\u00a0Olympics\\u00a0after missing out on Rio 2016 and Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2372, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.117531300039908e-22, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 2438, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9989951228990255, \"rank\": 0.0010053601769958165, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another gold medal would tie him with Carmelo Anthony on three golds and one bronze.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carmelo_Anthony\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0